RaftRPCCommand
public static final class RaftRPCCommand.Serializer
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonSerializer<Command>

JsonSerializer that uses a user-supplied CommandSerializer to convert a POJO Command instance into a base-64-encoded string. This class must only be used in conjunction with RaftRPCCommand.Deserializer. Both the CommandSerializer and CommandDeserializer must be set using RaftRPC.setupCustomCommandSerializationAndDeserialization(ObjectMapper, CommandSerializer, CommandDeserializer).
